                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10274" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1178</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">293 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亨通光电：在全球价值网络中的技术创新“突围”之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengtong - A Breakthrough in Technological Innovation in the Global Value Network</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴晓波，姚琳，张仪楚，雷李楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏亨通光电股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全球价值网络；生态替代；创新生态系统；行业引领者；2025百优案例；重点项目4-3</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Global value network, ecological substitution, innovation ecosystem, industry leader</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在当今全球经济深刻变革的背景下，中国制造业虽然凭借规模优势参与全球价值链，但在核心技术和关键环节仍受制于人，亟需实现从“边缘参与者”向“核心主导者”的转变。本案例以国家级单项冠军企业江苏亨通光电为研究对象，基于价值链升级三阶段模型（“技术替代-生态占位-构建标准”）和价值网络动态演化理论，揭示其从技术追随者向生态主导者转型的特殊路径。亨通光电作为中国光通信行业的领军企业，不满足于传统产业链的纵向整合，而是以生态化思维重构创新路径，突破国际巨头在核心技术上的垄断。公司通过“生态替代”战略，逐步实现关键技术的自主研发，建立了完整产业链布局，推动自主创新生态系统的形成。其技术突围之路包括自主研发光纤和光纤预制棒、突破封锁，成功实现技术自主，填补国内空白；基于纵向价值链在各关键链条节点进行合作、收购和资源整合等活动，形成围绕关键节点的创新生态群落；而后逐步演进形成创新生态系统，赋能其实现了核心关键技术的突破、攻坚与引领，并逐步由技术追随者转变为行业引领者。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of profound changes in the global economy, although China&#39;s manufacturing industry participates in the global value chain by its scale advantage, its core technologies and key links are still subject to others, and it is urgent to realize the transformation from &quot;marginal participant&quot; to &quot;core leader&quot;. This case takes Hengtong, a national-level single-champion enterprise, as the research object. Based on the three-stage model of value chain upgrading (&quot; technology substitution - ecological occupation - standard construction &quot;) and the dynamic evolution theory of the value network, it reveals the special path of its transformation from a technology follower to an ecological leader. As a leading enterprise in China&#39;s optical communication industry, Hengtong is not content with the vertical integration of the traditional industrial chain. Instead, it reconstructs the innovation path with an ecological mindset and breaks through the monopoly of international giants in core technologies. Through the &quot;ecological substitution&quot; strategy, the company has gradually achieved independent research and development of key technologies, established a complete industrial chain layout, and promoted the formation of an independent innovation ecosystem. Its technological breakthrough path includes independently developing optical fibers and optical fiber preforms, breaking through blockades, successfully achieving technological independence, and filling domestic gaps. On this basis, activities such as cooperation, acquisition and resource integration are carried out at each key node of the vertical value chain, forming an innovation ecosystem community around the key nodes. Then, it gradually evolves to form an innovation ecosystem, empowering it to achieve breakthroughs, breakthroughs and leadership in core and key technologies, and gradually transforming from a technology follower to an industry leader.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）价值网络的定义及企业在其中的角色定位；（2）创新生态系统的定义及后发企业的组织系统演化阶段；（3）生态位能力的内涵及提升路径；（4）自主可控布局创新生态系统的重要性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10274" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看案例使用说明</th>
